titles.title: Xi Ge Xi Mei: Kaixin Leyuan

data.title: Xi Ge Xi Mei: Kaixin Leyuan
Dushi Miao Qitan
data.synopsis:
A story about the cat demons Nighteye and William who, through trading with humans, absorb the soul of the trader to increase their life span via cultivation and become immortal. In these transaction, interesting stories happen with Hong Yu, Lan Ling and others.

(Source: ManhuaTai)
